quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  41,26,"wqal alkafirun baeduhum libaed mtwasyn fima bynhm: la tasmaeuu lhdha alqran, wala ttyewh, wala tnqadu lawamrh, warfeu 'aswatakum balsyah walsfyr waltkhlyt ealaa muhamad 'iidha qra alqran; laealakum tghlbwnh, fytrk alqra't, wnntsr elyh"
  41,27,"flndhyqn aladhin qaluu hdha alqawl edhabana shdydana fi aldunya walakhrt, walanajzianahum 'aswa ma kanuu yaemalun min alsyyat"
  41,28,"hdha aljaza' aldhy yujza bih hwla' aladhin kafaruu jaza' 'aeda' allah alnar, lahum fiha dar alkhulud aldaym; jaza'an bima kanuu bhjjna wadltna yajhadun fi aldnya. walayt dalt ealaa ezm jarimat min sarf alnaas ean alquran alezym, wsdhm ean tdbrh whdayth bay wasilat kant"
  41,29,"wqal aladhin kafaruu biallah wrswlh, wahum fi alnar: rabana 'arina alldhayn 'adalaana min khalaqak min aljini wal'iins najealhuma taht aqdamna; liakuna fi aldark al'asfal min alnar"
  41,30,"'in aladhin qaluu rabuna allah taealaa wahdah la sharik lh, thuma astaqamuu ealaa shryeth, tatanazal ealayhim almalayikat eind almawt qaylyn lhm: la takhafuu min almawt wama bedh, wala tahzanuu ealaa ma tkhlfwnh wara'akum min 'umur aldnya, wa'abshiruu bialjanat alati kuntum tueadun bha"
  41,31,"wataqul lahum almlaykt: nahn ansarkm fi alhayat aldnya, nsddkm wnhfzkm bi'amr allh, wkdhlk nakun maeakum fi alakhrt, walakum fi aljanat kula ma tashtahih 'anfusakum mimaa tkhtarwnh, wtaqarr bih aeynkm, wamahma tlbtm min shay' wjdtmwh bayn 'aydikum dyaft w'ineamana lakum min ghafur ldhnwbkm, rahim bkm"
  41,32,"wtqwl lahum almlaykt: nahn ansarkm fi alhayat aldnya, nsddkm wnhfzkm bi'amr allh, wkdhlk nakun maeakum fi alakhrt, walakum fi aljanat kula ma tashtahih 'anfusakum mimaa tkhtarwnh, wtaqarr bih aeynkm, wamahma tlbtm min shay' wjdtmwh bayn 'aydikum dyaft w'ineamana lakum min ghafur ldhnwbkm, rahim bkm"